The tuwangis are unacceptably irritating and rebellious.

You must kill the {@LinkCreature:5#1#tuwangi overseers}, {@LinkCreature:5#2#helpers}, and {@LinkCreature:5#3#workers} in Babok Hollow.

Report to Gara in the Marshlands when your mission is complete.
Excellent! I love seeing these numbers go up and up!

You know this is where you turn things in, yes? Not to pick things up?

No, no reason. I was just making conversation.
